            significance of \(3.7\sigma\). The relative branching fraction of \(B^{-} \to \Lambda_{c}^{+} 
            \bar{\Lambda}_{c}^{-} K^{-}\) with respect to the \(B^- \to D^+ D^- K^-\) decay is measured to be 
